Imprisoner/Predator/Choran:



With the two other robots inside of him, Imprisoner hovered over a long 
stretch of ocean as he speeded off towards the coast of Brazil, South America.

"Your sure the ship is coming?"

"Yes, of course I'm sure!" Choran yelled to the disembodied voice of 
Imprisoner.  "I wouldn't have said anything otherwise."

"We can't go, we haven't collected any bounties.  Our partners will kill us."

"Predator, shut up." Imprisoner replied.  "I am the leader of that bounty 
hunter guild and they will do as I say.  We killed two Maximals at least, and 
put some hurt on the Maximals.  And we have much needed reconaissance on that 
planet.  Not much news has been going back and forth.  And with the knowledge 
we've acquired, we'll break even."

"Sure." Predator sighed.
